{"tid":946620,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【【盤點無牌作品十大反派!!!】】","createTime":"2018-12-18T15:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T18:50:45.000Z","uid":46717,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"55321b630956d59120359c84d5f80a9e2f8a598c","tid":946620,"uid":46717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:52:23.000Z","msg":"1.最終木久<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/18/DMon8L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2FDMon8L.jpg&h=5e6dadf1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n鎧甲武士最後反派,到五星陣同神龍刺青仲有出場<br />\n2.駱駝<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/18/tM9sdF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2FtM9sdF.jpg&h=1ee9f34b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呂良偉同青山才子頭號敵人,害死大量好人,到神刺97回被亓哥殺死<br />\n3.錢不安<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/18/grJjIw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2FgrJjIw.jpg&h=f73b38ed&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n初出場在五星陣故事116,到神刺時期成為葉精信最後死敵<br />\n4.東方妖人<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/18/V7CsLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2FV7CsLA.jpg&h=2cd747b5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n格劍中環保組織藍色和平成員,想毀滅地球所有人類<br />\n5.基斯克里<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/18/1NnjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2F1NnjAi.jpg&h=abdbd690&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n曾經殺死呂良偉,被曹缺殺死後好似改邪歸正?<br />\n6.癲公<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/18/RAIeJg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2FRAIeJg.jpg&h=a305b247&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n獲黃頭號敵人,打極也不死,目前為止有6個形態,可能會有更新變身<br />\n7.終極生命體<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/18/QftFoa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2FQftFoa.jpg&h=3bfb9c5d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n粉俠傳最強反派,只有一歲,非常年輕<br />\n8.偽曹缺<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/18/1FpLxR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2F1FpLxR.jpg&h=49210596&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n跟粉俠傳主角曹缺一模一樣的人,非常難對付!!<br />\n9.魏王<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/18/0fyLY8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2F0fyLY8.jpg&h=236a13fd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n晉國英雄傳2,3最後BOSS,最後死在青龍手上<br />\n10.最後大佬<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/18/OzP2DV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2FOzP2DV.jpg&h=3a4309e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n粉俠傳最終BOSS,被曹缺父女打敗,退出江湖"},{"pid":"efe20f6f069cf3c5f839c895015aa29065646292","tid":946620,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:59:07.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce79a7813f83884b600f4fca9ff9b4b67a804a9","tid":946620,"uid":46717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"efe20f6f069cf3c5f839c895015aa29065646292","tid":946620,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:59:07.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:03:51.000Z","msg":"太少人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05ad440e5239e89052a6092c969c2ebe8b5d700","tid":946620,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ce79a7813f83884b600f4fca9ff9b4b67a804a9","tid":946620,"uid":46717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"efe20f6f069cf3c5f839c895015aa29065646292","tid":946620,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:59:07.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:03:51.0